# 2p_meet — client walks LEFT toward the col-55 wall, jets over.
# Pairs with 2p_meet.host.shot. Same screenshot ticks for direct
# host-vs-client comparison.

window 1280 720
out build/shots/net/meet_client
network connect 127.0.0.1:24051
name ClientB

at 150 press left
at 320 press jet
at 380 release jet
at 380 release left
at 440 press left
at 470 release left

at 200 shot match_start
at 320 shot walking
at 400 shot jetting_over_wall
at 520 shot meet_t520
at 580 shot meet_t580
at 700 shot summary
at 750 end

contact_sheet sheet cols 3 cell 320 180
